description: Table containing data about electrical A/C compressors, which can be tested by test bench MS112

columns.name: MSG SKU
columns.description: This column represents the MSG Article of the compressor.

columns.name: OEM
columns.description: This column represents the list of corresponding OEM numbers of original manufacturer

columns.name: Part number
columns.description: This column represents the list of part numbers for this compressor

columns.name: Car
columns.description: This columns represents the list of compatible vehicles for this compressor

columns.name: Cables and fittings
columns.description: This column represents the list of compatible cables (high-voltage cable with suffix H and data cable with suffix D), fittings (suffix HP for high-pressure fitting and LP for low-pressure fitting) and special repair tools

columns.name: Protocol
columns.description: This columns represents the type of protocol for this compressor
